PfiQueueAction is a BusinessClass
    owned by pfi
    prefix is PfiQA
    default label is "QueueAction"
	disable data area copy

    Ontology
        symbolic key is PfiQueueAction

    Patterns
        implements CRUD
        disable AsOfDateProcessing
        disable Auditing
        disable EffectiveDated
        implements IncrementalReplication
            indicator field is IsReplicated
                replicate when false
                    then set to true

    Persistent Fields

        ActionTaken is a PfiActionTaken
        PostAction  is Alpha size up to 500
        ShowReasonPopup is Boolean
        IsReasonCodeRequired is Boolean
            default label is "ReasonCodeIsRequired"
        IsReasonCommentRequired is Boolean
            default label is "ReasonCommentIsRequired"
        Subject is Alpha size up to 200
        IsReplicated is Boolean
            default label is untranslatable

    Derived Fields

        TranslatedAction is a DerivedField
            type is Text
            if (PfiTranslationRel exists)
                return PfiTranslationRel.TranslatedValue
            else
                return ActionTaken

    Relations

        PfiTranslationRel
            one-to-one relation to PfiTranslation
            Field Mapping uses symbolic key
                related.PfiTranslation = ActionTaken

    Sets

        ByWorkunitActionTaken
            sql name is PfiQA01
            duplicates
            indexed
            Sort Order
                PfiWorkunit
                PfiActivity
                ActionTaken

        ByIsReplicatedUniqueID
            sql name is PfiQA02
            indexed
            Sort Order
                IsReplicated
                UniqueID

    Actions

        Create is a Create Action

        Update is an Update Action

            Exit Rules
                IsReplicated = false

        Delete is a Delete Action
